text: Frédéric Lancien (born 14 February 1971) is a French former cyclist. He competed in the track time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Concarneau Category:Sportspeople from Finistère
